// Test ta.highest and ta.lowest — the extreme VALUE over the window.
// Like Pine, na until the window has `length` bars. Over the last 3 bars close
// is 299, 300, 301.

// Bars: 3

high3 = ta.highest(close, 3)
log.info(high3)

low3 = ta.lowest(close, 3)
log.info(low3)

// Expected output:
// na
// na
// na
// na
// 301
// 299
